    ;;; Luke Gorrie <luke at bluetail.com>                                          
    (defun activate-peril-sensitive-sunglasses ()
      "With apologies to Zaphod Beeblebrox."
      (interactive)
      (mapc (lambda (face)
              (set-face-foreground face "black")
              (set-face-background face "black"))                                   
            (face-list)))

How easy it is to misread page titles. I give you, (drumroll...), !PerlSensitiveSunglasses!:

    (add-hook 'cperl-mode-hook 'activate-peril-sensitive-sunglasses)

; )

